title: Re: ‘That’ll show him’! Chelsea Handler’s act of defiance near WH not expected to bring down Trump presidency
text:
‘That’ll show him’! Chelsea Handler’s act of defiance near WH not expected to bring down Trump presidency Posted at 5:40 pm on February 9, 2017 by Doug P. Share on Facebook Share on Twitter 
Donald Trump expressing his displeasure with Nordstrom for dropping his daughter Ivanka’s brand caused Chelsea Handler & friends to show up at the White House with bags in hand: A Gay, a Muslim, and a Jew hit Nordstrom and then hit @WhiteHouse to give the finger to @realDonaldTrump . pic.twitter.com/kFu8qKvh0u 
— Chelsea Handler (@chelseahandler) February 9, 2017 
The Trump presidency is expected to survive that particular act of defiance: Liberals sure know how to stick it to The Man. https://t.co/mL7El6VZtt 
— Drew McCoy (@_Drew_McCoy_) February 9, 2017 That'll show him. https://t.co/9E4zebORcB 
— Eric Spencer (@JustEric) February 9, 2017 @_drew_mccoy_ @camedwards Pres. Trump must be signing his resignation as we type. 
— Brian Fettner (@brianfettner) February 9, 2017 They should try that in Tehran if they want to learn about oppression. https://t.co/SJcv3PZCYJ
